1
00:00:05,675 --> 00:00:08,371
<i>Press down hard on the gas</i>

2
00:00:08,445 --> 00:00:12,313
<i>That's right, there's no compromise</i>

3
00:00:12,382 --> 00:00:16,375
<i>We'll slip through the night</i>

4
00:00:16,720 --> 00:00:19,211
<i>At the final moment push hard</i>

5
00:00:19,289 --> 00:00:23,350
<i>That's right, all the way to zero,</i>

6
00:00:23,426 --> 00:00:27,385
<i>Until we wipe away the days</i>

7
00:00:28,865 --> 00:00:33,598
<i>Gently open your heart</i>

8
00:00:34,304 --> 00:00:37,273
<i>If you pull it close to you</i>

9
00:00:39,709 --> 00:00:41,802
<i>It will reach you, without a doubt</i>

10
00:00:42,545 --> 00:00:43,842
<i>It will come, closer</i>

11
00:00:44,180 --> 00:00:46,740
<i>Now</i>

12
00:00:54,791 --> 00:01:00,161
<i>We're speeding through life,</i>
<i>squeezing it for all of its worth</i>

13
00:01:00,363 --> 00:01:01,523
<i>Our feet are tied</i>

14
00:01:01,598 --> 00:01:05,398
<i>But we still keep going farther</i>

15
00:01:05,735 --> 00:01:10,934
<i>Even if I take it back, and grasp it</i>

16
00:01:11,207 --> 00:01:12,538
<i>If you're not the one</i>

17
00:01:12,609 --> 00:01:14,008
<i>There will be no meaning</i>

18
00:01:14,077 --> 00:01:20,346
<i>And so we'll go far off into the distance.</i>

19
00:01:35,943 --> 00:01:37,137
I'm going...

20
00:01:38,512 --> 00:01:39,740
to become the Hokage!

21
00:01:41,115 --> 00:01:43,413
I can't lose here!

22
00:01:44,385 --> 00:01:45,977
You? Hokage?!

23
00:01:46,187 --> 00:01:47,779
When you're weaker than me?

24
00:01:49,990 --> 00:01:53,551
I'll become... Hokage for you!

25
00:01:58,199 --> 00:01:58,927
Transform!

26
00:02:03,904 --> 00:02:05,371
Hey hey, are you serious?

27
00:02:05,539 --> 00:02:06,528
You've been here three years

28
00:02:06,607 --> 00:02:08,598
and you can't even do
a respectable transformation?!

29
00:02:09,243 --> 00:02:11,473
All of you watch now!

30
00:02:11,812 --> 00:02:16,181
I will absolutely someday become
the true and a real Hokage!

31
00:02:20,121 --> 00:02:22,715
Lame! What Hokage!?!

32
00:02:24,892 --> 00:02:29,056
You know deep down inside that
you can't become the Hokage.

33
00:02:29,764 --> 00:02:31,095
So quit acting tough!

34
00:02:32,833 --> 00:02:33,925
<i>You're wrong Kiba...</i>

35
00:02:54,088 --> 00:02:57,387
If you compete with me for
the name of Hokage...

36
00:02:59,527 --> 00:03:02,963
You... will be the loser!

37
00:03:03,664 --> 00:03:09,603
Surprise Attack!
Naruto's Surprise Weapon!

38
00:03:19,346 --> 00:03:22,474
Man! Same thing over and over again.
You're pesky!

39
00:03:27,121 --> 00:03:28,179
Well, never mind.

40
00:03:28,322 --> 00:03:32,452
I'll just make it so
you won't stand up again!

41
00:03:33,027 --> 00:03:33,823
Let's go, Akamaru!

42
00:03:34,862 --> 00:03:37,092
You think you can get me with
that same technique again?!

43
00:03:38,999 --> 00:03:39,624
Take this!

44
00:04:03,824 --> 00:04:04,950
<i>Damn!</i>

45
00:04:08,095 --> 00:04:09,722
<i>Fang Over Fang!</i>

46
00:04:15,436 --> 00:04:16,368
<i>This Jutsu...</i>

47
00:04:16,670 --> 00:04:18,228
<i>Though, I've seen it before...</i>

48
00:04:18,339 --> 00:04:21,137
<i>it's not a Jutsu you can dodge</i>
<i>over and over!</i>

49
00:04:22,042 --> 00:04:22,770
<i>What do I do?</i>

50
00:04:25,079 --> 00:04:26,944
<i>What should I do?!</i>

51
00:04:37,124 --> 00:04:38,989
Looks like you've got nothing left.

52
00:04:39,927 --> 00:04:41,326
I've got plenty left!

53
00:04:41,729 --> 00:04:45,722
Even if you increased yourself by
three or four, I'd still have a lot left!

54
00:04:47,134 --> 00:04:48,931
You've got a comeback
for everything!

55
00:04:49,270 --> 00:04:51,397
Let's finish him with the next!
Akamaru!

56
00:05:10,624 --> 00:05:11,386
Damn!

57
00:05:12,159 --> 00:05:13,990
I have to counterattack somehow.

58
00:05:17,231 --> 00:05:20,564
<i>Even if I do, it has to get Kiba</i>
<i>or there's no point!</i>

59
00:05:21,135 --> 00:05:23,660
<i>But which is which...?</i>

60
00:05:28,375 --> 00:05:30,309
W-What will you do? Naruto!

61
00:05:31,912 --> 00:05:32,606
<i>Naruto...</i>

62
00:05:38,118 --> 00:05:38,846
<i>T-That's it!</i>

63
00:05:42,289 --> 00:05:42,914
Transform!

64
00:05:48,095 --> 00:05:48,959
You're mine!

65
00:05:57,237 --> 00:05:58,602
I see how it is...

66
00:05:59,406 --> 00:05:59,963
Huh?

67
00:06:00,107 --> 00:06:01,665
There, look closely.

68
00:06:07,681 --> 00:06:08,238
Oh!

69
00:06:17,091 --> 00:06:17,955
You did it!

70
00:06:18,092 --> 00:06:19,957
That's a clever move, Naruto!

71
00:06:21,996 --> 00:06:22,724
Naruto!

72
00:06:23,631 --> 00:06:25,030
If he transforms into Kiba,

73
00:06:25,299 --> 00:06:29,030
the real Kiba doesn't know which is
Akamaru and which is Naruto...

74
00:06:29,803 --> 00:06:31,600
He can't attack carelessly.

75
00:06:32,473 --> 00:06:36,967
However, it's okay for Naruto
to attack either one!

76
00:06:37,111 --> 00:06:38,476
Oooh!

77
00:06:38,979 --> 00:06:40,844
He created a chance opening...

78
00:06:41,649 --> 00:06:42,411
Good work!

79
00:06:42,750 --> 00:06:44,980
<i>I see, so that's your move...</i>

80
00:06:45,552 --> 00:06:46,519
<i>But...</i>

81
00:06:47,588 --> 00:06:49,055
I'll give you a piece of advice!

82
00:06:49,957 --> 00:06:52,926
I was careless before and
a little late to realize it...

83
00:06:53,594 --> 00:06:55,789
But the Transformation Jutsu
isn't effective anymore!

84
00:06:57,398 --> 00:06:59,832
Why, you ask?

85
00:07:00,100 --> 00:07:01,465
Yeah!

86
00:07:06,006 --> 00:07:07,496
I can smell you.

87
00:07:09,109 --> 00:07:13,068
Don't mess with our
sense of smell, Naruto.

88
00:07:16,850 --> 00:07:19,648
<i>By concentrating his Chakra</i>
<i>into his nose,</i>

89
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:22,689
<i>Kiba's sense of smell is enhanced tens</i>
<i>of thousands times more than average.</i>

90
00:07:23,924 --> 00:07:27,291
<i>Of course, he can determine</i>
<i>people by their smell too.</i>

91
00:07:28,095 --> 00:07:29,289
Heh, I won!

92
00:07:31,999 --> 00:07:33,330
W-What?!

93
00:07:38,038 --> 00:07:39,005
<i>What's going on?!</i>

94
00:07:39,807 --> 00:07:42,799
<i>Kiba's nose got Naruto and</i>
<i>Akamaru mixed up?</i>

95
00:07:47,848 --> 00:07:50,783
<i>Damn! What in the world is going on...?!</i>

96
00:07:54,054 --> 00:07:55,919
Then you're Naruto!

97
00:07:56,123 --> 00:07:57,351
Messing with me!

98
00:08:02,362 --> 00:08:03,351
What?!

99
00:08:10,471 --> 00:08:13,872
<i>Well, this is coming from</i>
<i>the original prankster, after all...</i>

100
00:08:14,575 --> 00:08:15,371
<i>He's had it!</i>

101
00:08:28,322 --> 00:08:29,016
He did it!

102
00:08:31,391 --> 00:08:33,291
Naruto... Awesome!

103
00:08:49,743 --> 00:08:50,437
Damn it!

104
00:08:54,815 --> 00:08:55,782
<i>So that's it...</i>

105
00:08:56,750 --> 00:08:58,547
<i>Naruto, transformed into Kiba,</i>

106
00:08:58,619 --> 00:09:01,486
<i>was discovered by the real Kiba</i>
<i>with smell and hit...</i>

107
00:09:04,057 --> 00:09:06,958
<i>But Naruto didn't come back</i>
<i>in true Naruto form.</i>

108
00:09:07,161 --> 00:09:08,719
<i>Instead, he transformed into</i>
<i>Akamaru instantly!</i>

109
00:09:10,764 --> 00:09:13,062
<i>In order to make it look as if it</i>
<i>was Akamaru who was hit</i>

110
00:09:13,133 --> 00:09:16,466
<i>and his impersonation</i>
<i>transformation dissolved!</i>

111
00:09:17,137 --> 00:09:20,629
Was Naruto ever that smart...?

112
00:09:24,211 --> 00:09:25,337
You little...!

113
00:09:26,914 --> 00:09:29,280
Think hard about your Jutsu
before you use them!

114
00:09:29,683 --> 00:09:33,278
Because they'll be used
against you, stupid!

115
00:09:36,456 --> 00:09:38,822
<i>He's using my line, word to word...</i>

116
00:09:39,493 --> 00:09:42,394
<i>Arguing with this guy is only</i>
<i>a waste of time!</i>

117
00:09:42,963 --> 00:09:44,453
<i>Don't go at Naruto's pace...</i>

118
00:09:45,165 --> 00:09:45,961
<i>Calm down.</i>

119
00:09:49,169 --> 00:09:50,101
<i>Calm down!</i>

120
00:09:54,875 --> 00:09:57,901
<i>He can't actually keep up with</i>
<i>my movements yet...</i>

121
00:09:58,545 --> 00:10:00,911
<i>I still have the advantage!</i>

122
00:10:03,984 --> 00:10:06,578
<i>Look closely at Naruto's movements</i>
<i>and if there's an opening...</i>

123
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:09,953
<i>I can surely take him from</i>
<i>behind with the All Four Jutsu.</i>

124
00:10:11,158 --> 00:10:12,819
<i>Nothing to get flustered about...</i>

125
00:10:13,660 --> 00:10:16,720
<i>If I do this in a level headed manner,</i>
<i>it's a match I will most certainly win!</i>

126
00:10:17,564 --> 00:10:19,930
<i>Evidently your enemy</i>
<i>has become calm...</i>

127
00:10:20,567 --> 00:10:22,865
<i>Well, what will you do, Naruto...?</i>

128
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:30,003
So you've finally gotten serious, Kiba?

129
00:10:30,177 --> 00:10:33,271
Well then... I'll end this...

130
00:10:33,347 --> 00:10:37,943
with my new special technique
I've been saving up!

131
00:10:40,674 --> 00:10:43,837
So you've finally gotten serious, Kiba?

132
00:10:44,145 --> 00:10:47,205
Well then... I'll end this...

133
00:10:47,281 --> 00:10:51,274
with my new special technique
I've been saving up!

134
00:10:51,552 --> 00:10:52,484
What?!

135
00:10:54,522 --> 00:10:55,921
New special trick?!

136
00:10:56,590 --> 00:10:58,854
Huh? When did he?!

137
00:10:59,393 --> 00:11:02,829
Leave it to Naruto to hide
a new technique!

138
00:11:03,230 --> 00:11:05,698
What new special technique!

139
00:11:05,933 --> 00:11:07,457
That's obviously a bluff!

140
00:11:07,735 --> 00:11:11,136
You can test out whether
it's a bluff or not!

141
00:11:12,740 --> 00:11:14,605
<i>This hasn't changed since before...</i>

142
00:11:15,042 --> 00:11:16,509
<i>Don't let his pace get to you.</i>

143
00:11:16,977 --> 00:11:17,909
<i>Calm down!</i>

144
00:11:18,379 --> 00:11:19,573
Let's go!

145
00:11:20,548 --> 00:11:22,140
I don't know what kind of
technique this is but!

146
00:11:22,817 --> 00:11:24,682
I just won't let you do it!

147
00:11:32,159 --> 00:11:32,716
<i>Now!</i>

148
00:11:33,227 --> 00:11:35,627
Ninja Art of Beast Mimicry...
All Four Jutsu!

149
00:11:41,102 --> 00:11:41,568
Q-Quick...

150
00:11:45,973 --> 00:11:47,668
Why are you stopping?!

151
00:11:51,679 --> 00:11:52,475
Naruto!

152
00:11:53,147 --> 00:11:53,806
Naruto!

153
00:12:04,859 --> 00:12:06,986
Just as I thought, this is as
far as he will go.

154
00:12:12,266 --> 00:12:13,824
Stand up! Naruto!

155
00:12:15,536 --> 00:12:20,269
D-Damn! I don't even have time
to work up my Chakra!

156
00:12:21,609 --> 00:12:23,236
Hey hey! What's wrong?!

157
00:12:23,444 --> 00:12:24,240
Naruto!

158
00:12:32,953 --> 00:12:34,045
He's fast!

159
00:12:34,221 --> 00:12:34,949
It's no good.

160
00:12:35,089 --> 00:12:36,852
He doesn't have time to
form hand Signs!

161
00:12:37,391 --> 00:12:39,450
<i>There's too much of a difference</i>
<i>in their strength...</i>

162
00:12:40,094 --> 00:12:41,891
<i>It's impossible for Naruto, after all.</i>

163
00:12:47,234 --> 00:12:48,098
<i>Naruto...</i>

164
00:12:51,639 --> 00:12:53,698
D-Damn!

165
00:12:55,476 --> 00:12:57,410
Take this!

166
00:13:06,453 --> 00:13:07,181
<i>What?!</i>

167
00:13:07,588 --> 00:13:09,886
Take that!

168
00:13:24,071 --> 00:13:25,800
I'm going to be Hokage!

169
00:13:26,907 --> 00:13:30,365
I won't lose here!

170
00:13:30,444 --> 00:13:34,642
Whatever! You can't keep up
with my speed at all!

171
00:13:52,166 --> 00:13:54,430
Hey hey hey hey hey hey hey!

172
00:13:58,839 --> 00:13:59,771
Naruto!

173
00:14:05,579 --> 00:14:07,672
This is what it's like when
I really let it out.

174
00:14:18,192 --> 00:14:19,318
You understand, don't you?

175
00:14:19,660 --> 00:14:22,458
To me, you're merely...!

176
00:14:55,763 --> 00:14:56,957
I...

177
00:14:59,566 --> 00:15:00,157
<i>Huh?</i>

178
00:15:03,237 --> 00:15:04,932
Will absolutely not lose!

179
00:15:07,808 --> 00:15:10,641
That Naruto... He's a fighter.

180
00:15:10,711 --> 00:15:11,405
Yup.

181
00:15:12,146 --> 00:15:15,946
If I were Kiba,
I'd be sick of this already.

182
00:15:17,051 --> 00:15:21,147
It doesn't matter which anymore,
I just wish they'd settle it quickly.

183
00:15:22,089 --> 00:15:22,987
<i>Naruto...</i>

184
00:15:23,857 --> 00:15:24,755
<i>Fight!</i>

185
00:15:25,726 --> 00:15:28,395
Naruto! Use the new technique
or whatever!

186
00:15:28,395 --> 00:15:29,487
Just settle it!

187
00:15:29,730 --> 00:15:31,755
Naruto! Go for it!

188
00:15:41,709 --> 00:15:44,007
<i>I have to find some opening</i>
<i>in that damn Kiba...</i>

189
00:15:45,813 --> 00:15:47,542
You've got absolutely no effect on me!

190
00:15:47,881 --> 00:15:50,247
You've got spirit, I'll give you that!

191
00:15:51,719 --> 00:15:53,209
<i>He's close at his end...</i>

192
00:15:53,854 --> 00:15:55,082
<i>I'll settle it with the next one!</i>

193
00:15:55,589 --> 00:15:59,218
I'll make the new technique
explode no matter what!

194
00:15:59,827 --> 00:16:00,759
I won't let you!

195
00:16:02,329 --> 00:16:02,954
You're slow!

196
00:16:03,931 --> 00:16:07,025
Take this!

197
00:16:12,773 --> 00:16:13,398
Oops!

198
00:16:23,283 --> 00:16:25,148
<i>Fast movements and a keen nose...</i>

199
00:16:25,986 --> 00:16:27,954
<i>The Ninja Art of Beast Mimicry</i>
<i>turned out to be harmful...</i>

200
00:16:29,223 --> 00:16:31,157
<i>Right now Kiba's sense of smell</i>
<i>is tens of thousands times</i>

201
00:16:31,225 --> 00:16:32,920
<i>more powerful than normal...</i>

202
00:16:37,398 --> 00:16:37,955
<i>Well...</i>

203
00:16:38,031 --> 00:16:39,862
<i>That fart was probably</i>
<i>a freak accident, but...</i>

204
00:16:39,933 --> 00:16:43,494
<i>That's what you'd expect from</i>
<i>the number one unpredictable Ninja.</i>

205
00:16:43,904 --> 00:16:44,962
Naruto!

206
00:16:45,572 --> 00:16:47,301
Now's your chance!

207
00:16:48,742 --> 00:16:50,733
Damn!
I was straining too much...

208
00:16:51,311 --> 00:16:54,974
But now's the time to show
my new technique!

209
00:16:55,816 --> 00:16:57,443
Shadow Clone Jutsu!

210
00:17:01,121 --> 00:17:01,849
<i>Naruto!</i>

211
00:17:02,723 --> 00:17:05,123
Okay! The way you've torn me
apart up until now,

212
00:17:05,192 --> 00:17:06,557
I'll give it back all at once!

213
00:17:13,534 --> 00:17:15,468
D-Damn it!

214
00:17:22,509 --> 00:17:23,134
U!

215
00:17:27,147 --> 00:17:28,808
Zu! Ma! Ki!

216
00:17:40,060 --> 00:17:41,322
Naruto... Barrage!

217
00:18:00,614 --> 00:18:02,445
<i>A new technique, eh?</i>

218
00:18:05,953 --> 00:18:09,889
<i>Well, he was watching Sasuke's</i>
<i>technique a moment ago...</i>

219
00:18:17,064 --> 00:18:18,053
<i>Lion Barrage!</i>

220
00:18:19,299 --> 00:18:21,767
<i>For the record, the name</i>
<i>is a rip off, too.</i>

221
00:18:42,022 --> 00:18:44,252
The winner is Naruto Uzumaki.

222
00:18:44,825 --> 00:18:46,952
Ohhhh!

223
00:18:47,494 --> 00:18:48,722
Cha!

224
00:18:48,795 --> 00:18:50,228
Nice one!

225
00:18:50,364 --> 00:18:51,626
You did it!

226
00:18:52,366 --> 00:18:55,267
That Naruto beat Kiba!

227
00:18:55,869 --> 00:18:57,564
It's a major upset...

228
00:18:57,671 --> 00:18:58,399
Yup!

229
00:19:00,607 --> 00:19:01,130
<i>Yes!</i>

230
00:19:13,854 --> 00:19:17,517
<i>I'm...getting stronger!</i>

231
00:19:24,531 --> 00:19:26,123
That was easy!

232
00:19:28,835 --> 00:19:30,462
<i>W-What to do?</i>

233
00:19:31,305 --> 00:19:32,499
<i>What should I do...?</i>

234
00:19:37,945 --> 00:19:39,879
N-Naruto...

235
00:19:40,881 --> 00:19:43,349
Huh? Hinata?

236
00:19:43,550 --> 00:19:44,642
Did you say something?

237
00:19:49,356 --> 00:19:51,381
Ah, ah, ah...
Umm...

238
00:20:01,268 --> 00:20:01,893
Huh?

239
00:20:02,736 --> 00:20:03,532
<i>Hinata...?</i>

240
00:20:05,839 --> 00:20:07,272
What's this?

241
00:20:08,575 --> 00:20:09,769
It's an ointment.

242
00:20:10,911 --> 00:20:12,003
Why for me?

243
00:20:20,220 --> 00:20:22,051
Take it for her, Naruto.

244
00:20:23,790 --> 00:20:26,190
Hmmm. Okay!

245
00:20:26,460 --> 00:20:29,486
Thank you! You're nice, Hinata!

246
00:20:34,134 --> 00:20:36,432
<i>Kiba, it's nothing to be</i>
<i>embarrassed about...</i>

247
00:20:37,404 --> 00:20:39,702
<i>This kid was a really</i>
<i>strong opponent.</i>

248
00:20:55,856 --> 00:21:00,088
<i>You are taking this pretty easy,</i>
<i>aren't you, Lady Hinata...?</i>

249
00:21:05,765 --> 00:21:10,225
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

250
00:21:10,369 --> 00:21:18,708
<i>The clear, blue sky goes on and on</i>

251
00:21:19,712 --> 00:21:28,381
<i>The ocean spans limitlessly</i>

252
00:21:28,788 --> 00:21:36,627
<i>Please keep that smile on your face forever</i>

253
00:21:37,897 --> 00:21:43,301
<i>Or else I'll cry</i>

254
00:21:43,369 --> 00:21:47,396
<i>You won't have to search around you</i>

255
00:21:47,473 --> 00:21:51,034
<i>It's all ok now.</i>

256
00:21:51,377 --> 00:21:59,910
<i>Everyone is inside</i>
<i>this hand</i>

257
00:22:00,186 --> 00:22:05,385
<i>when you want to cry,</i>
<i>and you want to run away</i>

258
00:22:05,458 --> 00:22:09,861
<i>When you forget what happiness is</i>

259
00:22:09,929 --> 00:22:13,695
<i>Just sing.</i>

260
00:22:13,933 --> 00:22:19,098
<i>Light is born, and darkness was born</i>

261
00:22:19,172 --> 00:22:21,367
<i>The two are one</i>

262
00:22:21,474 --> 00:22:27,743
<i>Harmonia, feel the telepathy</i>

263
00:22:28,247 --> 00:22:33,344
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

264
00:22:37,678 --> 00:22:39,009
What's with that guy!

265
00:22:39,379 --> 00:22:41,745
Calling people failure and judging them!

266
00:22:42,015 --> 00:22:45,507
Blah blah blah blah blah blah!
Talking like a wise guy!

267
00:22:45,585 --> 00:22:46,745
I'm in a bad mood!

268
00:22:47,120 --> 00:22:48,849
Hinata, you say something!

269
00:22:49,022 --> 00:22:50,387
Get that guy!

270
00:22:50,924 --> 00:22:54,690
Show that guy that people
can really change!

271
00:22:55,395 --> 00:22:59,559
Next episode:
"Byakugan Battle: Hinata Grows Bold!"

272
00:22:59,900 --> 00:23:03,097
Go! Fight! Hinata!
